   [photo1.jpg] A Closer Look
   man tending a plant Through imaginative programs and through
   partnerships with schools and civic organizations, libraries and
   museums are unmatched in the variety and breadth of knowledge they make
   available to everyone. Take a closer look - check out our highlights of
   the month or see what's happening in your state and online.
